<h3>
2.8.1.1  Course Mangement For Teachers
</h3>

The <tt>Teacher</tt> button (3rd button from the top) opens up the teacher section which is shown in Figure 2 below. This view shows all of the courses the teacher teaches. To view the entry code for the course, the user must click on any course. This entry code is used for students to register for a course.
To delete a section of class, the user will click the <tt>minus</tt> button on the appropriate row. The <tt>More Details</tt> button will go to the Students view of the section.
