<h3>
2.8.1.2  Student Management For Teachers
</h3>
The <tt>More Details</tt> button (the left button on the row) opens up the Student Management View. This view has rows which represent a section which the teacher teaches. The last row is a row to add a new section to the teacher. To delete a student, the user would hit the <tt>minus</tt> button. To add a student, the user would hit the <tt>plus</tt> button on the left. The <tt>More Details</tt> button is represented by the three dots and when clicked, will show the test result details which is found in seciton 2.5.

